         'VDAC1 mean intensity (AU)\\n[Mitochondrial mass]'),
        ('mtco1_norm',  'MTCO1/VDAC1',
         'MTCO1/VDAC1 ratio\\n[Complex IV / Mitochondrial mass]'),
